thread.title: BRIEF-Genesee & Wyoming Reports Traffic For January 2018

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Genesee & Wyoming Reports Traffic For January 2018
text:
Feb 14 (Reuters) - Genesee & Wyoming Inc:
* GENESEE & WYOMING REPORTS TRAFFIC FOR JANUARY 2018 * GENESEE & WYOMING INC - TRAFFIC IN JANUARY 2018 WAS 277,131 CARLOADS, A DECREASE OF 1,137 CARLOADS, OR 0.4%, COMPARED WITH JANUARY 2017
* GENESEE & WYOMING INC - ‍G&W‘S TRAFFIC IN JANUARY 2018 WAS 277,131 CARLOADS, A DECREASE OF 1,137 CARLOADS, OR 0.4%, COMPARED WITH JANUARY 2017​
* GENESEE & WYOMING - ‍G&W‘S SAME-RAILROAD TRAFFIC IN JAN 2018 WAS 276,630 CARLOADS, A DECREASE OF 1,638 CARLOADS, OR 0.6%, COMPARED WITH JANUARY 2017​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
